Use the Basquio context pack before implementation.

Required reads:
- Basquio/docs/vision.md
- Basquio/docs/architecture.md
- Basquio/memory/canonical-memory.md
- Basquio/rules/canonical-rules.md

Hard rules:
- intelligence-first
- update decision-log and memory with architecture changes
- keep contracts in Basquio/code/contracts.ts in sync
- run pnpm qa:basquio after context edits
